data.title: John Wayne divorce, 1953
data.meta_description: 12 images. John Wayne divorce, 19 October 1953. Esperanza WayneJohn WayneFrank Belcher, AttorneyJerome Rosenthal, Attorney.Caption slip reads: "Photographer: Brunk. Date: 1953-10-19. Reporter: Santley. Assignment: Wayne divorce. 1-2: Esperanza Baur Wayne. 61: Photogs. and newshawks talk to Esperanza. 62-59-60: Esperanza Wayne. 57-58: John Wayne. 63: Frank Belcher, Atty.John WayeBo Roos (Wayne's business mgr.) entering City Hall. 64: Esperanza Wayne, and Atty. Jerome Rosenthal. 69-70: John Wayne, and his attorney, Frank B. Belcher."
